  "instructions": [
    "Combine cacao powder, orange blossom water, lemon juice, and vanilla powder in a blender and blend until smooth.",
    "Add coconut cream and blend until well combined.",
    "Add dates and blend until the mixture is silky and smooth.",
    "Heat almond oil in a saucepan over low heat.",
    "Add the cacao mixture to the saucepan and whisk constantly until the mixture is warm and silky.",
    "Remove the saucepan from the heat and stir in sea salt.",
    "Pour the mixture into individual serving cups.",
    "Chill in the refrigerator for at least 2 hours before serving."
